      <title>Simultaneous Q-Learning</title>
      <link>https://martagrz.github.io/project/simultaneous-q/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Feb 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://martagrz.github.io/project/simultaneous-q/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Multiple agents learning at the same time using a value-based approach leads to a non-stationary environment since it is constantly changing based on the opponent&amp;rsquo;s actions. I am investigating this system, including possible conditions on convergence and properties of this seemingly chaotic system.&lt;/p&gt;
